OL,6,FA drug addict who killed a dad-of-
OL,7,Fthree was caught while walking the
OL,8,Fvictim's labradoodle, Layla - two days
OL,9,Fafter he strangled him to death.
OL,11,FDonald Prentice Patience was found
OL,12,Fdead in his home after police were
OL,13,Fcalled to a suspected burglary when
OL,14,FIan Connell, 39, was seen walking away
OL,15,Ffrom property with his dog.
OL,17,FHe later told officers that the dog
OL,18,Fbelonged to his "mate Donald, who he
OL,19,Fworked for".
