OL,6,FConnell claimed Mr Patience instructed
OL,7,Fhim to break in to the home in , , in
OL,8,FAugust 2023 after snapping his key
OL,9,Ftrying to gain access to the property
OL,10,Fto walk the dog.
OL,12,FMr Patience was found at the bottom of
OL,13,Fhis stairs with his body stored inside
OL,14,Fa duvet cover after Connell attempted
OL,15,Fto move him upstairs.
OL,17,FA pathologist said it was likely he
OL,18,Fhad died two days before his body was
OL,19,Fdiscovered by officers.
