OL,6,FConnell, who told police he "loved Mr
OL,7,FPatience like a father", denied murder
OL,8,Fbut was found guilty after a trial at
OL,9,FManchester Crown Court.
OL,11,FConnell, of Duke Street, , is set to
OL,12,Fbe sentenced on 6 March 2024.
OL,14,FSpeaking to the judge after jurors
OL,15,Fleft the courtroom, he said: "I'm not
OL,16,Fguilty of this offence, Your Honour."
