OL,6,FMr Patience, originally from Alness,
OL,7,FScotland, moved to Greater Manchester
OL,8,Ffor employment but after a car
OL,9,Faccident in 2015 left him unable to
OL,10,Fwork - he turned to alcohol and
OL,11,Fpainkillers.
OL,13,FConnell who was a heroin and crack
OL,14,Fcocaine addict, said he became
OL,15,Ffriendly with Mr Patience and would
OL,16,Fcarry out work for him.
OL,18,FHe described the 45-year-old as his
OL,19,F'boss' and said he would give him
OL,20,Fmoney.
