OL,6,FProsecutors argued people including
OL,7,FConnell preyed upon Mr Patience's
OL,8,F"good nature" as he had access to
OL,9,Ffamily money.
OL,11,FThey believed Connell murdered Mr
OL,12,FPatience following a row over money.
OL,14,FProsecutor Michael Hayton KC told
OL,15,Fjurors: "Mr Patience was beginning to
OL,16,Flose patience with Mr Connell, and was
OL,17,Fnot as perhaps as receptive to
OL,18,Frequests for funds as he had (been) in
OL,19,Fthe past.
