OL,6,F"The Crown say this is the most likely
OL,7,Freason that today Mr Patience is no
OL,8,Flonger with us."
OL,10,FConnell was seen breaking into the
OL,11,Fproperty on Ainsworth Road, Radcliffe,
OL,12,Fby shattering a window in the kitchen,
OL,13,Fat 11am on 22 August.
OL,15,FWhen Connell was searched, Mr
OL,16,FPatience's driving licence and library
OL,17,Fcard was found in his pocket.
OL,19,FConnell claimed after taking drugs and
OL,20,Fwaking up he found Mr Patience dead on
OL,21,Fthe sofa.
